                     </row>
                  </table>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <seg n="u9758">☞</seg> the accuracy of this observation may be depended on.</p>
               <p>
Longitude of <name type="place" key="Fort Mandan (N. Dak.)">Fort Mandan</name> as deduced from the observation of the end of toal darkness when the eclips of the moon tok place the 14th of January Astronocl. 1805</p>
