         </div>
         <div type="entry">
            <sp who="jo">
               <speaker>Ordway</speaker>
               <ab>
                  <date/>
               </ab>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Monday 28th Jany. 1805</hi>. Clear and cold.    all hands employed cutting the Ice from round the Barge. Got large prizes<ref target="n09012803" n="3"/> &amp; attempted to Shake hir loose but found that we could not move hir without considerable more cutting or other means.


		
						


</p>
            </sp>
